Package no.uib.triogen.io.genotypes

Interface VariantIterator

All Known Implementing Classes:
CustomVcfIterator, SimpleGenotypeIterator, VcfGenotypeIterator, VcfIterator, VcfIteratorTargets
public interface VariantIterator
The variant iterator iterates through all the variants of a file.
Author:
Marc Vaudel

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type Method Description
    void close()
    Closes the iterator.
    int getnVariants()
    Returns the number of variants read from the file.
    boolean isFinished()
    Returns a boolean indicating whether the iteration is finished.
    GenotypesProvider next()
    Read the next variant.
